Datasheet
Smart Soft Starter Controller (ESP32 + Web Offline + RS485 Modbus RTU)
1) Deskripsi Produk
Smart Soft Starter Controller adalah modul kontrol soft-starter berbasis ESP32 untuk aplikasi motor/beban DC 24V.
Perangkat menyediakan:

kontrol soft-start/soft-stop,
proteksi arus/tegangan/suhu,
monitoring lokal via OLED,
monitoring & konfigurasi via Web UI offline (Access Point),
integrasi DCS/SCADA via RS485 Modbus RTU.
Dirancang untuk aplikasi industrial termasuk pemasangan dalam enclosure/explosion-proof box dengan akses monitor jarak dekat melalui WiFi AP lokal dan RS485.

2) Fitur Utama
Soft-start bertahap: 15V → 24V (step 0.5V)
Soft-stop terkontrol (ramp down)
Current limiter adjustable: 1.0A – 10.0A
Proteksi fault:
Over Temperature
Current Sensor Error
Over Current
Under Voltage Input
Fault logging (timestamp uptime)
Auto-retry setelah fault (enable/disable + delay + max retry)
LED status indikator + deskripsi status di Web
OLED realtime status lokal
Web HMI offline (tanpa internet/CDN)
RS485 Modbus RTU slave untuk DCS/SCADA
3) Spesifikasi Teknis
3.1 Kontrol & Komputasi
MCU: ESP32
PWM output: 25 kHz, 8-bit
State machine:
IDLE
SOFT_START
RUNNING
SOFT_STOP
FAULT
3.2 Input/Output
Digital input:
START button
STOP button
KONTAKTOR input (active LOW)
Digital output:
Relay control
Alarm output
LED Green / Red / Yellow
Analog input:
Current sensor
Input voltage sensing
Output voltage sensing
Temperature sensor:
DS18B20 (OneWire)
3.3 Parameter Operasi (default firmware)
Soft-start awal: 15.0V
Soft-start akhir: 24.0V
Step ramp: 0.5V
Interval step: 140 ms
Soft-stop duration: 3000 ms
Overcurrent delay: 300 ms
Undervoltage delay: 500 ms
Current limit: 1.0 – 10.0 A (default 8.0 A)
Temperature limit: configurable (default 80°C)
Min input voltage limit: configurable (default 18.0V)
3.4 Komunikasi
WiFi AP lokal
Mode: Access Point
SSID: SoftStarter-Config
Password: spektra2026
IP default: 192.168.4.1
Web UI: single-screen, realtime numeric monitoring
RS485 Modbus RTU
Physical: RS485 half-duplex
Default: 9600, 8N1
Slave ID: 1
Protocol: Modbus RTU slave (holding register map)
4) RS485 Wiring (Final Valid)
ESP32 TX2 (GPIO17) → DI (RS485 transceiver)
ESP32 RX2 (GPIO16) ← RO (RS485 transceiver)
ESP32 GPIO4 → RE + DE (digabung)
Bus: A→A, B→B, common GND disarankan
5) Indikasi LED
LED Hijau kedip: IDLE / standby
LED Hijau ON: RUNNING
LED Merah kedip: FAULT aktif
LED Kuning ON: SOFT_START / SOFT_STOP proses
6) Fault Code
0: Normal
1: Over Temperature
2: Current Sensor Error
3: Over Current
4: Under Voltage Input
7) Modbus Register Ringkas (Holding Register)
HR0: Command (1 start, 2 stop, 3 reset fault)
HR1: State
HR2: Fault code
HR3: Vin x100
HR4: Vout x100
HR5: Current x100
HR6: Temp x100
HR7: PWM
HR8: Current limit x100 (R/W)
HR9: Temp limit x100 (R/W)
HR10: Min Vin x100 (R/W)
HR11: AutoRetry enable (R/W)
HR12: AutoRetry max (R/W)
HR13: AutoRetry delay/10ms (R/W)
HR14: Fault count
HR15-16: Uptime seconds (32-bit)
8) Web API Ringkas
GET /api/status → status realtime
GET /api/settings → baca setting
POST /api/settings → update setting
POST /api/control → start/stop/reset fault
GET /api/faultlogs → baca log fault
POST /api/faultlogs/clear → clear log
9) Kondisi Operasi & Instalasi (rekomendasi)
Gunakan catu daya stabil 24VDC
Gunakan ground reference yang baik untuk sensor analog
Gunakan twisted pair + terminasi RS485 sesuai panjang jaringan
Untuk enclosure kedap/ex-proof:
pastikan manajemen termal internal memadai
sediakan prosedur akses service yang aman
Lakukan kalibrasi arus final setelah pengujian beban aktual
10) Batasan
Firmware default ditujukan untuk aplikasi 24V (sesuai scaling saat ini)
Akurasi arus bergantung sensor, noise grounding, dan hasil kalibrasi lapangan
Web AP dimaksudkan untuk commissioning/maintenance lokal
